<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, July 21 (Xinhua) -- The bodies of John F. Kennedy
Jr., his wife and sister-in-law have been located off the coast of
Martha's Vineyard in Massachusetts State of the United States,
days after Kennedy's plane crashed, government officials announced
Wednesday.
</P>
