wife, and her sister Lauren Bessette, 34, on a flight to Martha's
Vineyard from New Jersey State. After dropping Lauren Bessette off,
Kennedy and his wife were to continue to Hyannis Port to attend
the wedding of his cousin.
</P>
<P>
Several experienced pilots have said the hazy skies and
darkness were challenging even for them. Kennedy obtained his
pilot's license in April 1998. 
