Athens Flight Information Region (FIR) by Turkish warplanes.
</P>
<P>
In a written statement, Papandreou said that he condemned this
action, which did not aid the de-escalation of tension in the
relations between Greece and Turkey, at a time when the Turkish
government had officially expressed its will for an improvement of
the climate in bilateral relations.
</P>
<P>
The minister had ordered Greece's ambassador to Ankara to
protest strongly to the Turkish Foreign Ministry.
