<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, July 21 (Xinhua) -- Britain hopes a visit to London by
Russian Foreign Minister Igor Ivanov will mend a rift between the
two countries over NATO's military campaign in Kosovo, British
officials said Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
