<HEADLINE> Bangladeshi Organization Condemns Lee Teng-hui's Separatist Remarks </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
DHAKA, July 22 (Xinhua) -- The Bangladesh-China Cultural,
Economic and Mass Communication Center (BCCEMCC) seriously
condemned the separatist remarks made by Lee Teng-hui on
cross-Straits relations.
</P>
