its image as a cultural destination to the world, welcome the
country's guests, or join both the local and international
meetings on my behalf," said Paveena, who oversees TAT.
</P>
<P>
The ambassadors would also help demonstrate the talents of Thai
women and reduce unhelpful stereotyping, she said.
</P>
<P>
More campaign would be staged to encourage people who deal with
tourists, particularly taxi drivers and guides, to avoid steering
foreign visitors toward unhealthy activities. 
